_sText:
cs_twilight_2017 is a major edit from the original cs_twilight.

Edits include:
:: Every light in the level has been modified
:: Sprites added for every light
:: Extensive brushwork reduction/cleaning across the map
:: Texture changes to the sidewalk, road, some outside buildings
:: Beveled some outside buildings so they're not as flat
:: Fixed weird, unused parameters on entities across the map
:: Modified the 'secret' room to be open and feature information about the map
:: Increased lightmap scale in several areas
:: Re-designed both stair rooms
(Many more changes, that cannot be listed)

This map was compiled on -final -both with Orange Box parameters for best prop shadows. 
LDR and HDR cubemaps built.
